name: Henri Matisse's La Danse by Zaam #2
description: Dance (La Danse) is a painting made by Henri Matisse in 1910, at the request of Russian businessman and art collector Sergei Shchukin. It is commonly recognized as "a key point of (Matisse's) career and in the development of modern painting".  This is the second recreation of the dance by artificial intelligence as an homage to matisse’s brilliance. This ongoing project is a unique and single edition 1/1
